{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The leader in the room was a fellow by name of Hamek Schuldkraut from Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was older than most of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He already has been married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His-- he had a wife and child, who were killed during the creation of the Tarnow ghetto, before he was sent to us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "His wife refused to part with the child and they-- the child-- they shot the child in his wife's arms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a little more hardened and experienced.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was actually our, our, our leader.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was very talented, very gifted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He, he portrayed-- he-- with crayons he obtained in the plant, he portrayed the scenes from camp life, like issuing of food, you know, and lining up and [NON-ENGLISH] work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And our, our room was, was the neatest one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And whenever there was an inspection by SS or Red Cross, they brought them to our room, to show how, how, how well they treated the inmates.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were young fellows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We tried to. to, to keep ourselves neatly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One time while he was working, he worked in the power [? press ?] department, somebody moved the mattress, and the power-- the, the, the the stem broke.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And his number was taken down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We knew that he was going to be executed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The, the night before his execution, we knew that this time came because the fellow who was the grave digger, [NON-ENGLISH], was called out to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He dug several graves and came back, and told us that he dug graves for about 12 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that particular night, we knew that, next morning, they are going to come and take him out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That night, we all laid awake, at the beginning, to watch him, so he shouldn't run away, because we would be their next-- the logical victims.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
